data.description: 3 Bedroom, 2 Full bath home in Park Place, close to the Lake at White Oak Park! Living room has a cathedral ceiling & wood burning fireplace. Kitchen is open to the living room w/ stainless appliances. Brand new LVP flooring installed in 4/2024 in living room, kitchen & front landing. Dining room area has a built-in buffet. Upper level bathroom has a new vanity, mirror and flooring. New back deck & stairs installed and front handrail installed 4/2024. New siding installed in 1/2024 w/ the house freshly wrapped. All upper level windows replaced within the last 10 years. Furnace & AC are 2 years old. Water heater installed in 12/23. Washer/dryer will stay. Garage door replaced approx 4-5 years ago. This house is ready for someone to move right in!! Showings start on Saturday 4/27/24.
